" make < > shifts keep selection
vnoremap < <gv
vnoremap > >gv

" replace within selection only
vnoremap :s :s/\%V

" Ctrl+V (block select) is hijacked by windows terminal for paste
nnoremap cv <C-v>

" Panic Button
